adviseScripts.text: Mister, why do you keep staring at me like that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Do you really like my swimsuit that much?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, I love it.
It's all right, I guess.
I appreciate your honesty.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'm not going anywhere, so go ahead and keep looking.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Feel free to snap a photo while you're at it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Would you like me to pose for you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You're not being honest with me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You couldn't take your eyes off me earlier,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: and now you're acting like my swimsuit isn't much to look at?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: That doesn't make much sense, does it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I have a conversation about the swimsuit she's wearing.
Mmm, this is delicious.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Would you like to try some?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I made it myself.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Take a sip.
Down it in one gulp.
*Sip*
Well, well, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Seems you know your way around a drink.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: The taste changes as the ice melts,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: so take your time and savor it slowly.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: *Gulp gulp gulp*
Ahhhhh!
Wow.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I didn't think you'd down it in one shot.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Rosanna while having a drink.
I know you're supposed to strike a pose for the camera,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: but it's not really my thing,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: and I'm not sure what pose would suit me best.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Mind giving me your take on it, Mister?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna shows me several poses.
I think those cute poses really suit you.
I think confident and sexy poses really suit you.
... Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You can't be serious.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You're messing with me, aren't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Just as I expected.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: But hearing it from you, Mister,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: gives me even more confidence.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'll have to practice those poses more often, then.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I coach Rosanna on the types of poses that suit her.
Rosanna is carefully maintaining her surfboard with a serious expression.
Talk to her.
Wait for her.
Hey there, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You finally made it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Give me a moment.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'm in the middle of something important.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Soon after.
Did you wait for me, Mister?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: How commendable.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Come here.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I want to praise you for your thoughtfulness.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I have a conversation on how to take care of surfboards.
Mister, don't you ever get bored being alone?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Is there anything you'd like to do with me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Let's go surfing.
Let's build a sand castle.
I figured you'd be interested in that,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: so I brought an extra surfboard.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Let's go!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Today, we're going to get you riding a wave.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: What?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You mean the thing Sakura's been obsessed with lately?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: ... I am not really interested in that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Let's step out for a walk for now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna takes my hand and gently tugs me towards the beach.
*Sigh* This isn't easy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I've been giving Viper surfing lessons for days now,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: but her skills aren't improving at all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Do you have any brilliant ideas, Mister?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I could help you teach her.
How about starting over with the basics?
No.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I can say with absolute certainty that that's the worst possible idea.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: With you around, there's no way Viper can focus.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: But we started from the basics...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Oh.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I should start with teaching her how to balance on solid ground first.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Thanks for the advice, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I listen to Rosanna complain about Viper for a while.
What do you think is the most important aspect of surfing?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Balance.
Advanced tricks.
You really know your stuff, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It may seem easy, but it's not.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You've gotta nail that balance
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: to start riding the waves.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You seem to enjoy showing off, huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Not that there's anything wrong with that,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: but there are more important things to consider.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I continue to talk about surfing.
I'm having a tough time
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: getting used to this boisterous atmosphere.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Want to take a stroll with me?
You'll get used to it.
Sure.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'm always open to invitations for a date.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Where should we go?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Do you have somewhere in mind?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I seriously doubt it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I don't think I even want to get used to it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: *Sigh*... Let's take a walk to clear our heads.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I stroll around the island.
Those fellas over there
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: have been fishing all day.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Don't they get bored, just doing that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Would you like to try it out yourself and see if it's boring or not?
Don't you surf all day?
I'll pass.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Sitting around doing nothing and blankly staring at a fishing rod
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: doesn't exactly sound like my idea of fun.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'd only get antsy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I do. Why?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: That's essentially the same thing.
Aaah,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: so that's what they're into, huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I still find it amazing that they get so much out of sitting around doing nothing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I have a conversation about fishing.
This sand is so annoying.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It never comes off completely.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Why don't you use something other than your hands?
Why don't you wash it off with water?
Like what?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I proceed to use some talcum powder and a dry towel to brush off the sand.
*Wipe wipe*
Hmm?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It came off so easily.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I should have known you'd come up with something.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Thanks, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I always take a shower
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: when I get back to our accommodation,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: but I can never get them out completely.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I help brush off the sand that's stuck on Rosanna.
I had no idea Sakura brought a swimsuit like that with her.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: She must be awfully confident to wear something like that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, it was pretty.
Yours is more...
Hmm?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Prettier than the one I'm wearing?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Don't look away. Tell it to me straight.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: More what?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Haha.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Why's your face suddenly so red?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Oh, Mister, your reactions crack me up sometimes. You're adorable.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I talk about Sakura's swimsuit.
Look at this, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It's a seashell.
I ran into Mary by the beach earlier, and she gave it to me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: She said that if you put it up to your ear, you can hear the ocean.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Don't tell me you actually believed that?
Isn't the sound of the waves nice?
So it's not true?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: That's too bad...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: But...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: So she wasn't pulling my leg?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna puts the shell to her ear.
Yes,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: it sounds lovely.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It's not every day I get a gift, so I ought to take it with me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You know as well as I do that we can't just take things we find on the surface.
I know.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: As long as I'm careful though,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: there shouldn't be any issues.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna examines the shell for a long time.
Never imagined I'd lay eyes on the real ocean.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Life is full of surprises.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It sure is.
It's even better since you're here.
It's even better because all of us are here together.
I feel the same.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'm having a blast with you here, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Having the others around can be quite bothersome,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: but whatever.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'm not so sure I agree.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: If at all possible, I would have preferred it to be just you and me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I enjoy the view of the ocean.
Mister,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: what type of ocean view appeals to you the most?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: The ocean on a sunny afternoon.
The ocean at dusk.
That's not bad at all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Perfect for hitting the waves.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: But it’s not quite to my taste.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Heh, you do know a thing or two, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I also find the view of the ocean at sunset absolutely captivating.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It's so easy to
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: get sucked in by its beauty.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I continue to talk about the ocean view.
Did I overdo it with the surfing?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'm parched.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Do you have anything to drink, Mister?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Hand her an iced drink.
Hand her a cup of hot tea.
Ah,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: that hits the spot.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Thanks, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Are you kidding me with this?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'm not Sakura.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I have a conversation about what drinks she enjoys.
Mister, what's got you so fixated?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: The rose tattoo on your hip.
The rose tattoo on your arm.
Oh, this?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It shows that I'm the boss of Hedonia.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: My, my, how bold of you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Didn't think you'd be ogling at me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Oh, this?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It shows that I'm the boss of Hedonia.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: But is that the only one you've found?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I have more, you know.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Why don't you try finding them too?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I discuss the tattoos on her body.
Mister, can you help me apply sunscreen?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: There are a few places I can't reach myself.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Apply sunscreen to her back and waist.
Apply sunscreen to her thighs and calves.
*Slather slather*
That's it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Mmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: That feels nice.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Why don't you keep going and apply it to other areas?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: *Slather slather*
I already took care of those areas, Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I told you I need help with the areas I can't reach.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Try again.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I carefully apply more sunscreen.
*Click*
Hehe, you look so surprised. I like it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Still, why don't you try smiling?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Make a silly face.
Flash a bright smile.
*Click*
Hmm... That's a pretty goofy expression, even for you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Still, it could come in handy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I can use it to scare the others away and prevent them from clinging to you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: *Click*
Tee-hee.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Mister, why do you look so awkward when you smile?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: This one looks awfully cute, though.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I think I'll use it as my phone background.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: W-wait, I was just messing around!
Take another one!
Rosanna and I have an impromptu photoshoot.
You know the girl who's like a puppy and always follows Viper around?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: She never seems to get tired.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Maybe she's born that way.
Maybe she's really a puppy.
I know, right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Her athleticism is nothing to scoff at either.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: To be born with such vivaciousness... Fascinating.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: ... Mister.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I'll pretend I didn't hear that joke.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Next time, try something less hackneyed.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Rosanna and I watch Jackal tirelessly run on the beach.
Mister,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: how would you describe our current situation at the beach in one word?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Happiness.
Peace.
Hmm... You're right.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: You do look happy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I will say that my thoughts are slightly different, though.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Ah.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: Yes, exactly!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: It's so peaceful here
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: that I sometimes feel like I'm dreaming.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I didn't think it was possible for me to ever feel this way.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rosanna

adviseScripts.text: I spend a peaceful moment with Rosanna.
